Class ReplenishmentRequest

java.lang.Object
org.CSPT.sc2001_grp1_proj1.entity.ReplenishmentRequest
public class ReplenishmentRequest extends Object
Represents a replenishment request for a particular medicine, including its status, quantity, and requester details.
